ygData.messageBody:
I was adventuring in The gorge, and this little flying deamon attacked me, I freaked out at first, and then conned it, it was risky. Its name was Yymp the Infernal. We battled, and I successfull slew the beast. When looting I was suprised when I found a (I imagine) a very valueable piece of armor, a Minoutar Ribcage 16ac 5str 5 stm -9 cha. Nice stats i thought. I being a high elf cannot use this piece of equipment, human euridite and half elf only, bleah but I am going to keep it for a new character i think. So all of you who can use it, i would reccommend watching out for it, I imagine it is a very rare find.

Lady Dame Laurana Highwind
Paladin of the 21st rank
Allied Explorers Of Norrath
The Rathe
List Moderator
